{"tid":647464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"平壤時間5月5日起撥快半小時　統一兩韓時區","createTime":"2018-04-30T00:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T03:29:42.000Z","uid":39464,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cd93f931b836039e49c1db2b02a1e35f6d42b4f1","tid":647464,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180430/s00005/c6f300c0f619f1452fb9280961c4d3bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180430%2Fs00005%2Fc6f300c0f619f1452fb9280961c4d3bd.jpg&h=dbea2c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朝鮮官方通訊社朝中社報道，朝鮮最高人民會議常任委員會今日發布《關於改定平壤時間》政令，為統一兩韓時間，由下月5日起平壤時間撥快30分鐘，即與韓國標準時間相同。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，這是根據朝鮮勞動黨委員長、朝鮮國務委員會委員長金正恩的建議而改定朝鮮標準時間。金正恩日前和韓國總統文在寅舉行峰會時論及統一北南雙方的標準時間問題。金正恩說，看到峰會場所掛上分別指平壤時間和首爾時間的兩個掛鐘時心裏很難過，「讓我們首先統一北方和南方的時間」。<br />\n<br />\n朝鮮原本與日本、韓國一樣，使用「GMT+9」時間，但朝鮮2015年8月中自行調慢時區半小時，向全世界宣布改為「平壤時間」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180430/s00005/1525045348694\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180430%2Fs00005%2F1525045348694&d=iasvbpCkUkVJl2lTLqQ2pDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d6cdb83d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180430%2Fs00005%2F1525045348694&h=08e3064b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180430/s00005/1525045348694</a>"},{"pid":"fa7763d5a886dc4ce8812ec863dc894ceb0c28fc","tid":647464,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:39:18.000Z","msg":"撥慢9小時ok？"},{"pid":"cf1e9cdc75a79e64130cda0945bbb0d6393e7400","tid":647464,"uid":86756,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:40:34.000Z","msg":"垃圾金仔<br />\n姓金嘅面比你丟哂"},{"pid":"26c7f59f3db5f216001f987eedc1d4d8b4be3356","tid":647464,"uid":141151,"like